snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get to Work: Official Doctor Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Examine patients, deliver babies, perform surgery, and save lives with the Doctor career in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack.

Learn more: http://bit.ly/1zlh2rE

Explore new active careers in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack, available April 2015.
